name: Lone Rider
description:
God is with the morning warrior who shepherds his horse to support his family.

Even if you have to be alone on the hill of Tenau Hill.. Sumba, Indonesia.

Beautiful life is that simple.. Wake up early, ride to the hills.. enjoy the beautiful nature of Indonesia.
